data.description: Wonderful home with lots of room to spread out, sitting on a nearly 1/4 acre lot. This home is a short distance to most everything the great town of Creswell has to offer, parks, schools, shopping to name a few. The car port is partially enclosed and could make a great shop area, both front and back yards are fenced, a new roof was just completed. Large family and living room with primary bedroom on opposite side of home from rest of bedrooms. Fig, Braeburn Apple and Quice fruit trees here!!
